<div class="zm-item-answer-detail">
<div class="zm-item-answer-author-info">
<h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap">


<a data-tip="p$t$mali" href="/people/mali">马力</a>，<strong title="最美团队招 hi.zuimeia.com" class="zu-question-my-bio">最美团队招 <a href="http://hi.zuimeia.com" class=" external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer"><span class="invisible">http://</span><span class="visible">hi.zuimeia.com</span><span class="invisible"></span><i class="icon-external"></i></a></strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="5">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$wu-yi-fan-97-37" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/wu-yi-fan-97-37" class="zg-link" title="隔壁老王">隔壁老王</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$yopz" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/yopz" class="zg-link" title="Yop">Yop</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$liu-fei" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/liu-fei" class="zg-link" title="刘菲">刘菲</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="94000" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class="fixed-summary zm-editable-content clearfix"> 我们每个人都是在有限的条件限制下，尽力按照我们所知的和想象的，让事情朝着我们认为更好的方向发展。<br>1. 很多貌似做事很理性、很科学的人，往往只是他们自己或者别人认为的理性和科学而已；<br><br>2. 现实世界中，正确往往只能逼近，没法绝对；<br><br>3. 塞翁失马焉知非福？既要看现在，还要看趋势。<br><br>举个例子：当年“人多力量大”的政策导致了现在中国庞大的人口，这个决策是好是坏？什么时候是好，什么时候又是坏？ 
<a href="/question/19784847/answer/12953336" class="toggle-expand">显示全部</a>
<div class="fixed-summary-mask"></div>
</div>

</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
